   "source": [
    "**Percentile**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "a0e65284",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def assign_pct(X):\n",
    "    mp = {}\n",
    "    X_tmp = np.sort(X)\n",
    "    pct = []\n",
    "    cnt = 0\n",
    "    for v in X_tmp:\n",
    "        if v in mp:\n",
    "            continue\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            mp[v] = cnt\n",
    "            cnt+=1\n",
    "    for v in X:\n",
    "        pct.append(mp[v]/cnt)\n",
    "    return pct  "
   ]
  },
